{"tid":1163611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好撚逼好辛苦","createTime":"2019-05-20T14:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T18:25:04.000Z","uid":230681,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6c2fae79fce7d98d5bf7dcb35d367393783d31","tid":1163611,"uid":230681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:12:36.000Z","msg":"每日返學返工放學放工呢啲時間搭地鐵<br />\n特別係露天車站 啲人出尻哂汗<br />\n無視你車廂內明明已經無位<br />\n但仲係要老鏈都推入嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後佢地皮膚上面立痴痴既汗水<br />\n就全撚部同你啲皮膚互相磨擦<br />\n仲有腋下既體臭<br />\n架車一開 啲風一吹 <br />\n哇 真係屌佢十次老母都唔撚夠賠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好撚多人呀香港</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06cd38ef41a2a9715fd1bc5aba53ca8b1426ed7","tid":1163611,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"聽日落雨仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf968d9d523c7d6102059654e6177ffdaff0bab","tid":1163611,"uid":185049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:17:00.000Z","msg":"買車囉"},{"pid":"65b3e701314ec26b86d5258fdd08abaecc24743f","tid":1163611,"uid":230681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f06cd38ef41a2a9715fd1bc5aba53ca8b1426ed7","tid":1163611,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"聽日落雨仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T18:25:04.000Z","msg":"打算聽日留喺屋企廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}